\c 52
\s UNkulunkulu uzakhulula iZiyoni
\p
\v 1 Vuka, vuka\x + 51.9.\x*, wembathe amandla akho, Ziyoni! Yembatha izembatho zakho ezinhle\x + Eks. 28.2,40.\x*, Jerusalema, muzi ongcwele\x + 48.2. Neh. 11.1.\x*! Ngoba kakusayikungena kuwe futhi ongasokanga longcolileyo\x + 60.21. 35.8. Isam. 21.27. Jow. 3.17.\x*.
\v 2 Zithintithe usuke othulini\x + 60.21.\x*, sukuma, uhlale phansi, Jerusalema! Zikhulule\x + Zek. 2.7.\x* \add ku\add*zibopho zentamo yakho, ndodakazi ethunjiweyo yeZiyoni!
\v 3 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Lathengiswa\x + 50.1.\x* ngeze\x + Hlab. 44.12.\x*; njalo lizahlengwa ngaphandle kwemali\x + 45.13. 1 Pet. 1.18.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Abantu bami\x + Gen. 46.6.\x* behlela eGibhithe esikhathini sendulo ukuhlala njengabezizwe khona, njalo iAsiriya yabacindezela ngaphandle kwesizatho.
\v 5 Khathesi-ke, ngilani lapha, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthi abantu bami bathethwe ngeze? Labo abababusayo babenza baqhinqe isililo, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, lebizo lami\x + Hez. 36.20,23. Roma 2.24. 1 Tim. 6.1. 2 Pet. 2.2.\x* liqhubeka lihlanjazwa lonke usuku\x + 1.4.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho abantu bami bazalazi ibizo lami; ngakho ngalolosuku\x + 2.11.\x* \add bazakwazi\add* ukuthi yimi engikhulumayo\x + Hlab. 102.27.\x*; khangela, yimi.
\p
\v 7 Zinhle kangakanani\x + Nah. 1.15. Roma 10.15.\x* phezu kwezintaba inyawo zalowo\x + Efe. 6.15. Seb. 5.9.\x* oletha izindaba ezinhle\x + 40.9.\x*, omemezela ukuthula, oletha indaba ezinhle zokulunga\x + 40.9.\x*, ozwakalisa usindiso, othi kuyo iZiyoni: UNkulunkulu wakho uyabusa\x + 1 Lan. 16.31.\x*.
\v 8 Ilizwi labalindi bakho! Bazaphakamisa ilizwi, bahlabele kakhulu kanyekanye, ngoba bazabona ilihlo ngelihlo\x + 1 Kor. 13.12.\x*, lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* izabuyisa iZiyoni.
\p
\v 9 Qhamukani ngentokozo\x + Hlab. 98.4.\x*, lihlabelele kanyekanye, lina manxiwa eJerusalema\x + 58.12. 61.4. 44.26.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* isibaduduzile abantu bayo\x + 51.3.\x*, iyihlengile iJerusalema\x + 48.20.\x*.
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yembule ingalo yayo engcwele\x + 51.9. Hlab. 98.1.\x* emehlweni azo zonke izizwe, njalo\x + Hlab. 98.3. Mat. 28.19. Luka 3.6.\x* imikhawulo yonke yomhlaba izabona usindiso lukaNkulunkulu wethu.
\p
\v 11 Sukani, sukani\x + 48.20. 2 Tim. 2.21. 2 Kor. 6.17.\x*, liphume lapha, lingathinti okungcolileyo, phumani phakathi kwayo, banini ngabahlambulukileyo, lina elithwala izitsha zeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Ezra 1.7-11. Levi 22.2. 1 Pet. 2.9.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba kaliyikuphuma\x + Eks. 12.33,39.\x* ngokuphangisa\x + Eks. 12.11. Dute. 16.3.\x*, kumbe lihambe ngokubaleka, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* izahamba phambi kwenu\x + Mika 2.13. Eks. 14.19.\x*, loNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli uzakuba ngumvikeli wenu ngasemuva\x + Mika 2.13. Eks. 14.19.\x*.
\s Ukuhlupheka kwenceku yeN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 13 Khangela, inceku yami\x + 42.1.\x* izakwenza ngenhlakanipho, iphakeme njalo iphakanyisiwe\x + 53.12.\x*, iphakeme kakhulu.
\v 14 Njengoba abanengi babethithibele ngawe\x + Jobe 17.8.\x*; ukukhangeleka kwayo\x + 53.2,3. Hlab. 22.6.\x* kwakonakele kangaka, okwedlula loba nguwuphi, lesimo sayo okwedlula amadodana abantu.
\v 15 Ngokunjalo izafafaza izizwe ezinengi\x + Levi 4.6. Heb. 10.22. Hez. 36.25. Heb. 9.13,14.\x*; amakhosi\x + 49.7,23.\x* azayivalela umlomo wawo; ngoba lokho abangakulandiselwanga bazakubona\x + 55.5. Roma 16.25. Roma 15.21.\x*, lalokho abangakuzwanga bazakuqedisisa.
